reviewText: The show is amazing, but I think that it needs to be pointed out that this box set is NOT, in fact, the complete series. This is only a set of seasons 1-5 (as you can clearly see in the photo of the product). At the time of this writing, season 8 is currently airing. Adventure Time, from what I understand, is almost over, but not quite, and when it is, I believe that a complete series box set will be released. Right now, though, you've got this, and you can get seasons 6 and 7 separately.
It is not worth the money! You can get all 5 seasons for less than 100$ by buying them separately.
Exactly what my son wanted for Christmas
My grandson was thrilled with it.
This isn't the complete series. It is the complete SEASONS 1-5.
Clean simple box-set collection of all 5 seasons
I have two kids, and I bought this for myself. Love this show.

As everyone else mentioned, there is no digital code included. Personally, I don't mind but I can see how that can bother other people. Each season comes in its own respective case and Season 5 comes in two

My husband and I really enjoyed our evenings watching Adventure Time over the Summer. We are hoping that seasons 6-10 will come out in a similar box set. I would recommend the show to kids and adults. Our favorite episodes were those that followed a storyline (Marceline and the Ice King) versus the one off episodes.
Bought this for the digital copies IN THE TITLE. Neither the Dvd or digital copies were included.
I bought the blu-ray set, but this DOES NOT include the DVD or digital copy, although thats what it says in the title/description. Great show though, Im so glad I finally bought this.
I love Adventure Time! This is perfect for a gift or for yourself!
